data.title: Menard Co Illinois Birth Records
data.text:
Menard County Illinois

Register of Births, Book 1

1877 - 1903

This is a complete transcription of Book 1. All information was transcribed from the original documents. Names & locations were spelled as close to the original as possible.

No records for surnames beginning with the letters "Q" or "X" were found

A B C D E F G H I J K L M N O P R S T U V W Y Z Indexed, no record
